lux is not rooted in regions that are obviously dark in EUV and\nX-ray emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Aug 2017 01:18:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Sep 2017 23:43:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-18"}
